  "instructions": [
    "Preheat the oven to 300F (150C).",
    "Brown the lamb in the olive oil in a large clay tajine or Dutch oven over medium-high heat, then set aside.",
    "Soften the onion and garlic in the same pan, then add the allspice, cumin, coriander, paprika, salt, and pepper, and cook for 1 minute, stirring constantly.",
    "Add the chopped onion mixture to the browned lamb, along with the dates and 1 cup of water, and bring to a boil.",
    "Transfer the tajine to the preheated oven and braise the lamb for 2.5 hours, or until the meat is tender and falling off the bone.",
    "Remove the tajine from the oven and let it rest for 10 minutes before serving."
  ],
